# Changelog and PR workflow

Read [AGENTS.md](../../AGENTS.md) and [docs/contributing.md](../../docs/contributing.md) before changing this repo.

## Changelog (mandatory)

Update [CHANGELOG.md](../../CHANGELOG.md) under `## [Unreleased]` for every
user-visible change (features, fixes, API, integration docs) **in the same task** —
do not wait for the user to remind you. Mirrors outpost `AGENTS.md` / pre-PR checklist.

## Pre-PR

- Run `npm run validate` when preparing a PR.
- Update README when public API or integration requirements change.
- Never stage secrets or `.env` files.

## Publishing

Never run the publish workflow or `npm publish` unless the user explicitly requests it.
